---
description: Checklist before finishing any page UI
globs: "**/app/**/*.tsx"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Page Checklist

- [ ] Title + primary action clear
- [ ] Loading state
- [ ] Empty state (no fake data)
- [ ] Error state + recovery
- [ ] Success feedback for mutations
- [ ] Responsive (mobile usable)
- [ ] RTL layout correct (widths mirrored)
- [ ] Keyboard + focus visible
- [ ] Permission/access handled
- [ ] Matches existing page chrome (header, spacing, components)
